```xml
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    package="com.madhub.facebookbulkpostingt">

    <!-- 
        This AndroidManifest.xml file configures the Facebook Bulk Posting Tool, 
        a powerful automation tool designed for efficient social media management 
        on the Facebook platform. This application empowers users to schedule 
        and manage their posts seamlessly using MadHub's advanced automation features. 
    -->

    <!-- Required permissions: -->
    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.INTERNET" />
    <!-- 
        This powerful permission enables the application to access the internet, 
        allowing it to communicate with Facebook's APIs for content management and 
        scheduling features. Essential for real-time operations and updates. 
    -->

    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE" />
    <!-- 
        Comprehensive capability for monitoring network connectivity. 
        This ensures the application can function smoothly by verifying 
        network availability before attempting to post content. 
    -->

    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE" />
    <!-- 
        This permission allows the app to save data locally, enabling 
        users to store media and content efficiently before posting. 
        This flexible configuration option enhances user experience 
        by managing media files effectively. 
    -->

    <application
        android:allowBackup="true"
        android:icon="@mipmap/ic_launcher"
        android:label="Facebook Bulk Posting Tool - Android Automation Tool"
        android:roundIcon="@mipmap/ic_launcher_round"
        android:supportsRtl="true"
        android:theme="@style/Theme.AppCompat.Light.NoActionBar">

        <!-- MainActivity serves as the entry point for the application -->
        <activity
            android:name=".MainActivity"
            android:label="Facebook Bulk Posting Tool"
            android:exported="true">
            <intent-filter>
                <action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
                <category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
            </intent-filter>
        </activity>
        <!-- 
            MainActivity is designed to provide users with a graphical interface 
            for managing their Facebook posts. It utilizes MadHub's no-coding 
            configuration, allowing users to set parameters for content scheduling 
            effortlessly. 
        -->

        <!-- AutomationService runs background operations for posting automation -->
        <service
            android:name=".AutomationService"
            android:exported="false">
        </service>
        <!-- 
            AutomationService is responsible for executing automated tasks in the 
            background, ensuring 24/7 operation capabilities. It leverages MadHub's 
            robust automation features to manage and schedule posts efficiently, 
            allowing users to maintain an active social media presence without manual 
            intervention. 
        -->

    </application>
</manifest>
```

This `AndroidManifest.xml` is designed to highlight the capabilities of MadHub in the context of a Facebook bulk posting tool while adhering to the specified guidelines and maintaining a feature-first approach in comments.
